T* (- Formatting requirements: Specify your preferred structure. Example sections include) Tj
T* (Project Overview, Features, Installation, Usage, Tech Stack, and Key Takeaways.) Tj
T* (- Tone and style: Describe whether you want it concise or detailed, technical or accessible.) Tj
T* (- Output rules: Instruct the tool to use Markdown, include code block placeholders, and) Tj
T* (format headings consistently.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Step 4: Upload Reference Files) Tj
T* (Upload your example READMEs and tech stack document to the project or custom GPT.) Tj
T* (This gives the tool persistent access to your style and preferred language.) Tj
T* () Tj
