T* (Drop in a quick summary of a recently completed project or lab. Review the generated) Tj
T* (README. Check formatting consistency, tone, and completeness. Iterate on your) Tj
T* (instructions if needed.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Step 6: Use It Weekly) Tj
T* (Each time you finish a project or lab, open the tool, paste in your summary or code) Tj
T* (snippets, and generate the README. Copy the output directly into your GitHub repository.) Tj
