T* (support this. Standard ChatGPT conversations do not.) Tj
T* (- File upload capability: You need to be able to upload your example READMEs and tech) Tj
T* (stack reference. Both Claude Projects and Custom GPTs support file uploads.) Tj
T* (- Markdown formatting: Ensure the tool can output clean Markdown with headings, code) Tj
T* (blocks, and lists. All major AI tools handle this well, but test with one example to confirm) Tj
T* (output quality.) Tj
T* () Tj
